<view class="feedback-screen">
  <view class="feedback-header">
    <image class="feedback-header-icon" src="/assets/icons/chat-bubble.png" mode="aspectFit" />
    <text class="feedback-title">帮助与反馈</text>
    <text class="feedback-subtitle">提交本地报告反馈后返回“我的”，不会调用线上服务。</text>
  </view>

  <view class="feedback-card">
    <view class="section-label">
      <image class="section-icon" src="/assets/icons/success-check-green.png" mode="aspectFit" />
      <text>报告体验</text>
    </view>
    <view class="rating-row">
      <text class="rating-chip active">有帮助</text>
      <text class="rating-chip">不清楚</text>
      <text class="rating-chip">不准确</text>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="feedback-card">
    <view class="section-label">
      <image class="section-icon" src="/assets/clean-icons/document-list-purple.png" mode="aspectFit" />
      <text>反馈标签</text>
    </view>
    <view class="tag-row">
      <text class="tag active">决策清晰</text>
      <text class="tag active">下一步清楚</text>
      <text class="tag">需要更多解释</text>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="feedback-card">
    <view class="section-label">
      <image class="section-icon" src="/assets/icons/idea-bulb-soft.png" mode="aspectFit" />
      <text>补充说明</text>
    </view>
    <view class="feedback-textarea">
      <text>本地反馈：完整报告解锁后，请保持下一步练习建议清晰。</text>
    </view>
    <text class="feedback-note">提交动作仅写入本地 mock 存储，用于测试证据。</text>
  </view>

  <button class="feedback-submit" data-action="my" bindtap="onTap">提交并返回</button>
</view>
